	This beautifully fragranced oil based shower scrub is deeply hydrating and skin softening for use in the shower. Made with sweet almond oil, pure black pepper and lime essential oils to stimulate and refresh, this beautiful shower scrub has a juicy, fruity accord of cranberries and zesty lime with supporting fruity notes of strawberry, raspberry, plum, peach, apple and cassis with hints of white flowers on a woody base. This gorgeous shower scrub comes in a beautifully decorated plastic tub making it a wonderful gift idea, or a perfect treat for you. Directions for use: Stir well before use. Scoop a small handful of scrub into your hands and apply to your body with a light circular scuffing motion, then wash it thoroughly from your body after use.&nbsp;</p>
